Titolo: Archon II: Adept

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Archon II: Adept is a 1984 action-strategy video game developed by Free Fall Associates' Jon Freeman, Paul Reiche III and Anne Westfall, and published by Electronic Arts for various platforms. Adept is a hybrid of a tactical board game and action. Although it does not have the chess motif of the original Archon: The Light and the Dark, it retains the central concepts of good vs. evil, one-on-one combat, magic, and power points.

Genere: Turn-based strategy

Valutazione: N/A
